This repository previously contained a git submodule at path "methodist-booster"
but lacks a .gitmodules entry. To simplify GitHub Pages publishing, we vendor the
current contents directly into the repository. If you need to switch back to a
submodule, restore a proper .gitmodules with the submodule URL and run:

 git submodule deinit -f methodist-booster
 git rm -f methodist-booster
 git submodule add <url> methodist-booster
